ActUnited Nations Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Regulations Implementing the United Nations Resolutions on Iran
PrecisRegulations Amending the REGULATIONS IMPLEMENTING THE UNITED NATIONS RESOLUTIONS ON IRAN give effect in domestic law to the sanctions set out in UN Security Council Resolution 1929 of June 9, 2010, which are necessary for Canada to fulfill its international legal obligation to implement the decisions of the Security Council.
